Title: Long Distance Tyler
Plot: Milo and Gibbs have a date-off with a beautiful woman. Tyler and Rachel try to stick together through the hassles of a long-distance relationship. Neal and Amy suffer the consequences of allowing Tyler to use their apartment as a rendezvous location.
